title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - September 24, 2021
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - September 24, 2021
description:
Gary and Mark link up to discuss the federal arrest warrant issued for Gabby Petito's fiancé Brian Laundrie and what the specific charges indicate. They also give up update on Evander Kane and more.

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
